#. module: beauty_parlor
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:beauty_parlor.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"After the treatment is completed, updating Emily’s opportunity status to Treatments Completed in the CRM\n"
"                  will automatically send her an email suggesting her next appointment."
